This paper focuses on computer vision tasks such as monocular depth estimation, camera ego-motion estimation, and optical flow estimation, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper deals with autonomous driving, which falls under robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses unsupervised learning, which is a popular topic in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper mentions the KITTI dataset, which is commonly used in computer vision and machine learning research related to autonomous driving (cs.CVPR).
